data.description: Welcome to 5762 Sweet Desiree, a home in the gated community of the Terraces at Alamo Ranch! This Incredible brick and stone, 1.5 story home lies on a massive corner lot with amazing curb appeal! Upon entering you will be greeted by a large foyer with high ceilings and 18 X 18-inch tile throughout the main living areas. The kitchen is very spacious with an oversized island and a built-in desk. The primary bath has a double vanity with a separate tub & shower combination and a large walk-in closet. Upstairs you will find an extra-large flex space with a full bath and walk-in closet. This room could serve as a game room, bedroom, office, gym, or theater room! One of the best features of this property is the oversized lot and backyard. Here you will find a huge, covered patio for relaxing and those family cookouts with a yard that has plenty of space for the kids to run around. Don't miss out on this gem, schedule your showing today!
